text: Beautiful one-level Cordata home with fantastic designer upgrades. Custom chefs kitchen with tall white shaker cabinets, Bosch S/S appliances, marble and glass backsplash, and a full-drawer spacious island that makes entertaining a dream. Stunning floor-to-ceiling stone fireplace, 9 ceilings, quartz countertops, under-mount sinks, and engineered wood flooring throughout bring this home to a whole new level of luxury living. Custom upgrades include an ironwood, wrought iron rail front porch, A/C, Maxx tub, fully tiled baths, designer lighting, a 52 backyard deck, and Xeriscape landscaping for effortless yard maintenance. Nothing here is builder-grade! If you've been looking for the one you have found it!

Welcome to your new home. Meticulously maintained home. Fantastic bonus room upstairs near the bedrooms. Outside you have a great yard, relaxing deck for entertaining in the summer and don't miss the husky hut for the fall football games. Great central location and Bellingham schools. Close to Lake Whatcom and Galbraith Mtn trail system.

This luxury home centrally located in Bellingham is ready for it's new owners! Walk into your open concept living room, dining, room and kitchen with a walk-in pantry. The oversized patio boasts sun throughout the day and is adjacent to protected land for extra privacy! Your two car garage has an extra storage nook with plenty of room for your bikes or a small workshop. Walk up the stairs (don't miss the peek-a-boo Mt Baker view!) to your primary bedroom. This oversized primary has an en suite bathroom and his and hers walk-in closets. Down the hall you will find an additional full bathroom, laundry room and two additional bedrooms. Don't miss out on this stunning home close to I-5, Cordata Park, Dining, Shopping & More!

Welcome to your dream home in the exclusive gated community of Semiahmoo! This stunning 1 story residence features 3 spacious bdrms & 2 modern bathrooms, perfect for comfortable living. The home boasts a beautifully remodeled kitchen with top-of-the-line finishes, ensuring a delightful cooking experience. Freshly painted exterior adds to its charming curb appeal, while a new deck in the back provides an ideal space for outdoor entertaining. The beautifully landscaped yard, equipped with a sprinkler system, enhances the home's serene ambiance. Additionally, the oversized garage offers ample storage & parking. This meticulously maintained property is a rare find in a sought-after neighborhood. Don't miss out on making this your forever home!

Mt. Baker view property. Large centrally located site with development potential. Currently in open space so build your home on this large property and pay low annual taxes. Irrigation rights for livestock or agriculture. Minutes to Ferndale or Bellingham. Easy I-5 access.

Top-floor corner unit in the heart of Lynden! Stunning views of Mount Baker and farmlands from the spacious private deck. One of the two bedrooms features a Murphy bed and built-in shelving and drawers. Solid wood cabinets and brand new vinyl flooring in kitchen/dining and bathroom. The Solatube skylight provides ambient natural daylight in the kitchen. In-unit washer & dryer is included (washer is brand new). Brand new water heater. Comparatively low HOA dues cover water/sewer/garbage. One assigned parking space plus ample guest parking. No rental cap.

Own a charming, affordable cabin nestled in a serene forest setting. This home sits on a spacious, level lot at the end of a cul-de-sac, offering privacy and tranquility. Enjoy modern updates like new stainless steel appliances and a newer roof (2022). The sunny, fully fenced yard provides a safe and peaceful outdoor space. Inside, a stackable washer and dryer maximize efficiency. Relax in the cozy loft after a long day. Perfect as a starter home or Airbnb, this property is near the beautiful Mt. Baker National Forest and just 45 minutes from Mt. Baker Ski Area. Bellingham is 35 minutes away, and the Sumas border crossing is 20 minutes. Your peaceful forest escape awaits!

Wow over 1 acre this close into town. Mostly flat land w/ detached garage w/ shop space & detached shed for all your lawn care items. This home has been lovingly cared for and is move in condition. It is a blast from the past era & is waiting for new owners to add your creative updates. It has 3 large bedrooms w/ primary having direct access to courtyard. Main living room leads to family room with gas fireplace for those cozy winter nights. Kitchen and dining room have ample cabinets, counter space and room for table and bar stools. Seller willing to leave all appliances for new owners. Extra 1/2 bath off laundry room as well as gas furnace. The yard is awesome w/ vast room for your custom shop? RV? Boat? Toys? Other vehicles?

Superior custom built home. 3 bedroom 2 bath on a large quiet lot. Many built in alcoves and custom features throughout. Brilliant living room with coffered ceilings and oversized windows allowing views to the private backyard. Bright kitchen with garden window and spacious breakfast nook. Extremely roomy master suite with walk through closet, jetted tub and separate jetted tub. You'll be pleasantly comfortable walking on the radiant floor heating system with multiple zones. Recently painted inside and out, new tile flooring , appliances and more! Oversized 576 s.f. 2 car garage and attic trussed for extra storage. Don't miss the bay and mountain views from the outside roof height deck.

Classic, timeless and traditional single story rambler offers an incredible 2, 500 sqft of living space. It's amazing how perfect the room size is in this home from the warm and inviting great room to the formal dining room. The private & sunny wrap around deck makes for a back yard of low maintenance living. Great exposure offers lots of natural light. Spacious kitchen is ideal for entertaining with easy access off the formal dining & breakfast nook. Excellent counter space & wonderful storage through out. The two car garage is extra deep. Two private guest suites, separate art studio with private entrance off the primary suite. Comfortable primary bedroom with sitting space, walk-in shower & custom closets. Exceptional value--a must see.

This lovingly maintained Holidaire trailer has everything you need for a cozy and relaxing get away. Curl up inside where warm wood tones create an inviting retro vibe. Outside, enjoy nature under the large covered custom patio, or sit around the campfire. A shed sits on the property for additional or larger storage. The Glen is zoned recreational for 120 days of use out of the year and has all the amenities you could want, including 2 pools, hot tub, tennis court, library, laundry mat, 2 clubhouse, 24 hr security, gated entry, & play areas.

This fully permitted vacant lot is located on a private cul-de-sac in the lakeside neighborhood of gate-2 in Sudden Valley - right behind Lake Louise. Permits are completed and paid for at Whatcom County and Sudden Valley - so begin your new construction project anytime after June 1st - while the Lake Whatcom Watershed is open for new development. The approved split entry house plan totals 1, 977 square feet and has 3 bedroom, 2 3/4 bathrooms, Living Room and a lower Family Room. Roomy 2-car garage. The property is just a short walk from the 1 mile long Lake Louise Trail. Territorial views toward Lake Louise looking up the cul-de-sac. All permits can be transferred to the new owner.

1, 500 square foot (30x50) industrial/storage condominium conveniently located in the Irongate Industrial Business Park. Quality built with steel construction and metal roofs for longevity and low maintenance in mind, and a gated community, STOREHOUSE, that is secure and accessible 24/7. Features include an ADA bathroom, large 14x16 overhead door with windows and automated opener, high vaulted ceiling, wired for 220 and additional outlets, lighting, shelving, epoxy floors, and so much more. Why rent when you can own.

Come home to luxury living on gorgeous Lake Samish with ~90 feet of lake frontage! Custom-built in 2012 and thoughtfully designed to maximize ease of life on the lake! Every detail is thoughtfully considered, from private balconies off of bedrooms & office, to the expansive main deck that includes entertaining & grilling space, to the private dock & low-maintenance landscaping. Air conditioning and fire suppression system throughout, and hot water on demand. ADU over garage w/ exterior access, 1BD/1BA, kitchen + living, W/D in unit. Basement includes space with kitchen, 2 BD/1 BA + laundry; potential to add wall to create a separate apartment. Just 20 minutes to downtown, this beautiful home offers the best of south Bellingham living!

Opportunity to own a unit in one of downtowns most convenient locations! This building offers an interior courtyard, secure entry, a large secure parking garage and an elevator. This 2-bedroom one bath unit has an oversized sliding door in the living room which floods in tons of natural light. Just a couple blocks from the Saturday market and walking distance to the university makes this a versatile home for anyone. With no rental cap this could be considered for an investor's portfolio as well. Don't miss out on the chance to be in the heart of all that Bellingham has to offer!
neighborhoods: City Center Bellingham, Downtown District Bellingham

text: Private end unit overlooking the 18th fairway of the Sudden Valley golf course. Loft bedroom with 2 full baths, recessed lighting, tile floors plus a private covered balcony. Vaulted ceilings provide lots of natural light. The condo is within walking distance of the golf course, restaurants and trails. Area amenities include 24/7 security, swimming pool, library, marina, tennis courts and more.

Discover a rare opportunity nestled just off Barkley Boulevard, boasting stunning views of the Bay and City of Bellingham. This spacious residence spans over 1800 square feet, featuring 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths upstairs, a 3/4 bath downstairs, and generous dining space leading to a fully fenced backyard. The third bedroom upstairs is versatile, easily transformable into an office space, featuring a sliding door granting access to the deck, providing unparalleled views of the Bay. Enjoy direct access to neighborhood trails and the convenience of Barkley Village shopping center just minutes away.

Expansive city, bay & mountain view from this better than new King Mountain stunner! Radiating PNW charm, the sun drenched interior delights with light & bright on-trend finishes and the open concept design sought after by the modern buyer. The main level primary suite is privately tucked away from the other bedrooms & features vaulted ceilings, a luxurious en-suite bath & spacious walk in closet. Convenient office/den is ideally located on the main level and you'll love watching the sunsets from your deck or quickly accessing the neighborhood park. Additional bedrooms and bonus space on lower level + unfinished area with potential to be a 4th bedroom or...you decide! Loads of storage throughout + fully fenced yard.

Welcome to your beach home in Birch Bay! Just steps from the beach, this charming corner lot property offers a glimpse of the bay and an ideal setting for relaxation or an AirBnB investment. The sun-filled living room boasts luxurious vinyl floors, perfect for cozy gatherings. The main floor features a comfortable bedroom and a modern 3/4 bathroom. Upstairs, you'll find three additional spacious bedrooms and a full bathroom, with the primary bedroom offering direct access to a private deck. Enjoy the beauty and tranquility of Birch Bay living, where every day feels like a vacation. Don't miss this opportunity to own a piece of paradise!

Wonderful single level home just a minutes walk to Lake Louise. Located in Gate 2, on a HUGE level lot, it will be hard to find a better 3 bedroom, 2 bath home. Featuring an open floor plan with vaulted ceilings, two living spaces for flexibility in living and large 2 car garage with tons of room for storage. The huge back deck encompasses the entire back of the home and is perfect for enjoying outdoor living and entertaining. Behind the home is a large shed, ideal for those outdoor projects and those individuals with a green thumb. Just minutes away is access to multiple Lake Whatcom beaches, parks & trails, and Sudden Valley Golf Course. The community had a pool, sports courts and a marina to provide some extra fun in the summer months!

This 1944 square-foot home offers a spacious sanctuary with 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, 2 inviting sitting areas, and a bonus room situated above the garage.Abundant natural light floods the interior through large windows and skylights, creating a bright and airy atmosphere throughout.Storage is plentiful, catering to organizational needs with a large pantry and under stairs storage.The new generator capable of powering the entire house, ensuring peace of mind during inclement weather or power outages.The kitchen, a chef's dream, features a top-of-the-line gas stove and is designed for culinary creativity with plenty of counter space and storage for kitchen gadgets and appliances. This well cared for home also backs onto a green belt...Privacy!

Welcome to this fully fenced garden oasis nestled in Cordata's Springs, Built Green solar community. This home offers breathtaking territorial views of Mt. Baker from its sunny southwest-facing position. Home features 3bedrm, 3bathrms, and a spacious 2-car garage at the end of a peaceful cul-de-sac. Equipped with 10 solar panels and a mini-split system for heating and cooling, home ensures energy efficiency. Ethernet wiring supports a robust home network, and the garage is prepped for electric vehicles. Enjoy upgraded kitchen appliances, expansive community open spaces, and neighborhood parks. The HOA takes care of the front yard lawn and shrubs. Easy access to major retailers and amenities.

If a thoroughly contemporary experience with outstanding access to trails and all the eateries and conveniences offered by Fairhaven are important, there really isnt a good reason to look further than this 2016 built 3 bed 2 bath masterpiece. After the guest depart, the entire upstairs is a primary suite, complete with private deck and steam sauna/shower!

Freshly updated & ready for new owners. You'll fall in love with this charming single level home right in the heart of Bellingham! Within walking distance to parks, trails, schools, Trader Joes, Sunnyland, & so much more. The new cedar fence gives the backyard great privacy. Large storage shed & an attached 2 car carport. Move-in ready!

Fully fenced and gated single level 3 bedroom 2 bathroom home. Positioned high above the 6th hole of beautiful Birch Bay Village's private golf course w/HUGE panoramic views of Mt. Baker, Course Ponds, San Juans, the Bay & more from almost every room. Escape to the serene woods of Point Roberts to this well-maintained home featuring 2 beds and 2 baths. Great building lot - Private and sunny south facing. It has been partially cleared and improved with two culverts, horseshoe driveway and leveled building site. Extraordinary 3 bed, 2.75 bath custom-built home nestled on a sunlit cul-de-sac lot, boasting breathtaking mountain views. A stunning home, known as the Jewel of the Neighborhood. Fully updated & customized, yet retains the charm of its era. Main bath w/soaker tub. Primary bedroom/bath w/walk in shower. Baker. 2 bedrooms 1 & 1/2 baths. Possible 3rd bedroom. 3 out buildings. Fenced back yard. 15 minutes from the Peace Arch border crossing into Canada.

Brand new highly upgraded home located adjacent to one of Sudden Valley's largest waterfront parks - Morning & Afternoon Beach. Enter the massive living / great room & enjoy 12 foot ceiling, luxury plank flooring, gas fireplace, and a large covered deck at the rear of the home overlooking Morning Beach Park. The platted trail down to the lakeside park is adjacent to this home. Kitchen offers high-end stainless appliances (gas cooktop), walk-in pantry, and 8' island with quartz countertop. Downstairs features Primary suite w/large ensuite walk-in closet & amazing full bath with large tiled shower, 2 guest bedrooms, den / family room, & a massive recreation room w/full wet bar & bar refrigerator. 2nd deck below with access to the trail.

Nestled along the scenic fairways of the golf course, this spacious 3700+ sq ft custom-built one owner home is now available for the first time. This generous 3-bedroom home hosts 2 ensuites, with additional living space and office upstairs. Enjoy the architectural marvels like vaulted ceilings and large windows that flood the home with natural light, serene views and wildlife. With its thoughtfully designed layout, this home provides the perfect canvas for your personal touches. Enjoy comfort and style in the vibrant community offering amenities - private beaches, seasonal pool, parks, gym, marina, & the 18-hole championship golf course.

New Modern Construction home in Lynden. This Luxury home has 4 bedrooms, 3.5 bathrooms, 2 living rooms, office, 2 primary bedrooms w/ attached elegant bathrooms, walk in tiled showers & walk in closets, the primary bedroom upstairs has a private deck with mountain view. Elegant Kitchen with lots of cabinets, stainless steel appliances, soft close cabinets, Quartz, Spice kitchen with oven, sink, Dishwasher, cabinets. Large Dining area with lower covered deck so you can access your large back yard. stone wrapped gas fireplace in the lower living room, upstairs living room with deck out back that spans the length of the back of the house. House has Solar installed, EV Charger installed, on one of the largest lots. close to Vancouver. Finished

Desirable ground floor WATER VIEW condo in Jacobs Landing! This 880sf 2 BD 1 BA unit works perfectly for a full-time residence, beach getaway, or short/long-term AirBB/VRBO rental. Completely remodeled recently with all NEW kitchen cabinets, appliances, flooring, bathroom tile, fireplace, doors, light fixtures, & more! Take in the fabulous ocean view & sunsets from your living room or walk out onto your garden patio with beautifully landscaped grassy area & just steps directly to the beach. Enjoy Jacobs Landing amenities including an indoor pool, hot tub, private clubhouse, tennis & racquetball courts. PLUS boating, crabbing, clamming, walking the berm & nearby restaurants. Centrally located in Birch Bay, minutes to 1-5 and US/CAN border.

Welcome to Bay Crest, one of Birch Bay's most desirable neighborhoods, where beach-town living is at its finest! This spacious 2, 138 sqft home features 4 bedrooms, an upstairs recreation room, and a roomy 3-car garage. Enjoy easy access to the beach via a short trail just across the street, and relax in the fully fenced backyard complete with a fire pit and patio, ideal for summer gatherings. Meticulously maintained and pre-inspected, this home also boasts updated appliances and flooring. The upstairs laundry room provides convenience for all bedrooms, while the primary suite offers privacy, a large walk-in closet, and an en-suite bathroom. Move in and enjoy a delightful summer in this exceptional home!

10 acre lot adjacent to Galbraith Mountain trails yet close to schools, shopping, I-5 Lake Padden and Lake Whatcom. Marketable timber is included. Currently no access. Current zoning is 6 units per one acre, buyer to confirm. Great parcel for recreation or come build your dream home!

The gorgeous acreage you've been waiting for is here! Located on a flat, cleared, shy-5-acre parcel, this beautifully updated 3-bed/2-bath home combines modern appeal with rural charm into one unique experience. Tree-lined driveway leads you to a cute single-level home with open layout, sunny kitchen with island + stainless steel appliances, and spacious primary suite with 3/4 bath and sauna! Recent updates include roof, deck, interior + exterior paint, carpet, concrete foundation skirting, and power to the 36' x 36' barn with loft and 3 stalls. Featuring garden space, fruit trees, and equestrian possibilities, there's something for everyone. Your piece of paradise awaits!

Northwest's excellent, level, creek-front building site. Lot #1 in the Glenhaven neighborhood. Glenhaven public water is available; a fire hydrant is right next to the lot. Wave Broadband Cable has high-speed internet service, and electricity is available in the street. Community features include a walking/hiking trail, two boat launches, two lakes, a clubhouse, a HUGE new inground public pool, tennis courts, a playground with swings, a sandbox, and more. Lots of great fishing in the two lakes. The community has a fishing derby every year!! This area has the option to access Burlington or Mt Baker Schools. Also, the building site is fully approved. Wetland mitigation and creek setback is approved.

Seize the chance to create your ideal retreat on Lummi Island, where this vacant lot awaits the realization of your dream home or cabin. The property is ready for construction, featuring a potential building site and the convenience of readily available utilities, including a two-bedroom septic system already in place. Enjoy the amenities Scenic Estates & Lummi Island have to offer, including access to a refreshing swimming lake, a saltwater boat launch, a private beach, and a clubhouse. Furthermore, revel in the serene backdrop as the lot abuts hundreds of acres of forested land.
nearby_schools: Lummi Elementary School, Ferndale School District, Lummi High School

text: Stunning west facing views of Vancouver Island, Semiahmoo Bay and the Strait of Georgia from this ultra luxury waterfront penthouse. Enjoy high ceilings, an intelligent open design, chef's kitchen with high end appliances, and a spa inspired bath in the primary suite. Floor to ceiling windows encompass the living room & primary bedroom. Immerse yourself in outdoor living year-round with a large, covered deck that is perfect for dining al fresco while enjoying spectacular sunsets, and all the activity the ocean has to offer. Embrace an active lifestyle adjacent to the renown Semiahmoo Resort with 5-star dining, biking, hiking, golfing, and a large marina with available slips. Don't miss this rare opportunity!

A masterpiece of design & construction. Nestled on a shy 5 acres, this Timberframe home boasts soaring ceilings & walls of windows that frame stunning views of Baker from nearly every room. Designed for culinary excellence, chef's kitchen fts a prep sink, granite counters & top-of-the-line Lacanche range. Main level living; primary BR fts luxurious en-suite w/clawfoot tub, bespoke tilework & abundance of natural light. Upstairs will greet you w/a lofted office/flex space, 2 BRs & updated bath. Brimming w/updates: newer roof, newer exterior paint, new interior paint, refinished hardwood floors, new carpet. Large shop/barn w/finished upstairs studio. Tranquil pond & manicured grounds create idyllic backdrop for hobby farm or horse enthusiasts

Private just shy of 5 acres near Galbraith Mountain is highly sought after and provides easy access to nature trails and recreational activities. Close to I-5, Lake Padden and all amenities. Currently no access, marketable timber is included.

One of 20 new homes by Skeers Construction in Hannah Creek. This is the ultimate PNW lifestyle location with access to 65+ miles of world class mountain biking, hiking, and trail running on the adjacent 3000 acre Galbraith Mountain trail system. Whatcom Falls Park is just down the street, and downtown is less than 3 miles away. This 4 bedroom plan features dramatic vaulted ceilings in the entry foyer, a main floor home office, and a covered patio for year round outdoor enjoyment. High tech energy features include innovative AeroBarrier building envelope air sealing, heat pump heating and cooling with energy recovery ventilation (ERV) system, and a super efficient hybrid heat pump hot water heater. Scheduled for July 2024 completion.

This beautiful 3 bedroom, 2 bath rambler is on a sunny lot at the end of a cul-de-sac. The light and bright central kitchen looks out in to the beautiful fenced backyard. Large deck and patio area for entertaining. Flex space off of the central kitchen can be used as an office, den or bedroom. Low maintenance yard with garden. Great walkability! Close to the Railroad Trail to Barkley Village, Roosevelt School and Whatcom Falls Park. RV parking.

Penthouse Condo w/ expansive, 180-degree views of Bellingham Bay, the City, Orcas Island & the Cascade Mountains! This 2 bed, 1.75 bath has an open floor plan, vaulted ceilings & numerous windows capture an abundance of natural light. Custom cabinetry, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances in kitchen & dining area. Sliding doors lead to a private balcony that captures the view of the Bay. Quality bamboo flooring, slate & ceramic throughout. Unit has Tankless H2O Heater, radiant heat throughout, and plenty of storage under stairs. Private entrance, spacious private patio & located adjacent to green space! Walkable location to parks, trails, schools & Downtown Bellingham! Unique opportunity for primary residence or potential rental.

The Lupine by MainVue Homes at Horizon is an expensive design you dont want to miss. The Outdoor Room is located at the front of the home, providing an all-season escape to enjoy sweeping mountain and ocean views. The Kitchen is flush with 3m Quartz counters, Stainless Steel appliances, designer lighting and a Grand Butlers Pantry w/garage access. Enjoy the open-flow layout between the Great Room, Gourmet Kitchen, and Dining Room & Multi-Purpose Room at the rear of the home. Upstairs, find the Grand Suite w/free-standing tub & walk-in shower, followed by the Leisure Room & three secondary bedrooms. Customer registration policy: Buyers Broker to visit or be registered on Buyers 1st visit for full Commission or commission is reduced.

Feel like you're living on vacation year-round in this well-maintained home, located in the beautiful community of Birch Bay Village. As you enter into the main living areas of the house, you will notice the vaulted ceilings with skylights and windows on every wall, allowing for natural light to fill the space. Brand new carpet throughout, this home feels fresh and clean. Primary bedroom overlooks the serene back yard, complete with an ensuite bathroom. The star of the show has to be the outdoor living area with a large covered deck, paved patio, studio, and garden with fruit trees - all backing up to a private field. It really is an outdoor oasis! Community features golf course, private beaches, pool, marina, sport courts & more!

Escape to your own slice of Pacific Northwest paradise with this 3-bedroom rambler nestled on just shy of 8 acres of pristine wilderness. Situated in a private enclave, this home offers unparalleled tranquility and seclusion, yet is conveniently located just 35 minutes from Bellingham. With close proximity to the mountains, trails, and lakes, outdoor enthusiasts will delight in endless recreational opportunities year-round, from hiking and biking to fishing and boating and skiing. This house is ready for you to make it your home.

Looking for privacy / serenity? Come take a look at this vacant lot located below the road, and in an amazing setting - with green-belt behind. The adjacent vacant lot to the right is owned by Sudden Valley and has been turned into permanent green-belt. The property is down-sloping, making it conducive for a home plan with main level living and a day-light basement. The slope in the building area is gentle, so you could also work with a normal 2-story home plan (going up). Enjoy a very peaceful neighborhood with territorial views over the green-belt and neighborhood. The neighboring property at 25 Rose Ridge Loop looks like it is in the permit process for a new home - which will enhance the neighborhood greatly.

Affordable opportunity to own a doublewide with an attached garage. The garage is extra deep which provides extra storage or makes a great workspace. Fenced back yard and garden shed too! Built in ramp into home for easy access. Open concept living area with vaulted ceilings. 2 bedrooms and 1 1/2 baths plus an office space. electric mini split for heat and AC Quiet community close to parks, library, shopping and restaurants.

This turn-key, lovingly maintained property backs up to a breathtaking view of the Nooksack river and surrounding mountains. Outside boasts a large cover deck and upgrades such as a new 1000 gal septic tank, updated gazebo, patio rails, wood storage, workshop, fenced side yard, and landscape lighting. Inside the bright and airy park model, youll find new stainless steel appliances, new furniture including a sleeper sofa, TV, chairs and tables, and a hot water heater added 2021. The Glen is zoned recreational for 120 days of use out of the year and has all the amenities you could want, including 2 pools, hot tub, tennis court, library, laundry mat, 2 clubhouses, 24 hr security, gated entry, & play areas.

Check out this very well maintained three plus bedroom rambler on a huge, quiet lot off a dead end street, with an oversized 2 car garage and many upgrades! The bright and sunny kitchen looks out over a back yard with fruit trees and raised bed gardens. New Vinyl Plank flooring throughout and a well positioned, efficient woodstove for those chilly nights. Classic utility room with a convenient half bath off of the garage. The big yard is partially fenced with extra space for an RV...and a tall carport in back for firewood or your toys. Plus, this is an easy walk to everything in town.

Come and see this updated unit in a beautiful 55+ community. It has been almost 2 years since the last 1 bedroom condo at the very desirable and private gated community of El Dorado went for sale. The unit has had major upgrades over the last few years including: in 2021 new kitchen appliances, the interior was painted, and new vinyl plank flooring was installed. In April of 2023 the seller purchased a new washer and dryer. For any storage needs, there is also a detached 1 car garage with remote control entry. This private community has a large clubhouse, 2 fully furnished guest rental units for the owners guests, a dog run, and a shared garden. Close to all the amenities you could possibly need, this unit is ready to go.

Nestled on a 365 day lot (rare!), reside in the picturesque seaside community in Birch Bay, just a short walk to the beach. Enjoy activities like clamming & sunbathing on a mile-long stretch of beach. This fully updated 2 bed, 1.75 Bath including a steam shower, situated in the secure Latitude 49 Community, renowned for its excellent association amenities. Features include a refreshing outdoor pool & spa, a mini-golf course, laundry facilities, & spacious clubhouse. Just minutes from the Canadian border. An additional lot (#112 - 180 day lot) is included for RV parking, both lots fully fenced, w/ 2 detached outbuildings w/ windows & skylights, providing a great work space or storage. Beautiful paved patio perfect for entertaining!

A rare opportunity to own a 3-bedroom home at an AMAZING price! This well-loved home boasts vaulted ceilings, open concept, bathroom and walk in closet of primary and ample natural light. Back patio entrance is off of the laundry room with a semi private back yard. Hidden Village RV park has a heated pool, community center, playground and beautiful pond. No age restriction community.

Beautifully well built 3 bed home with modern updates and style in the Village at King Mountain! Newer LVP flooring throughout the main floor, top of the line kitchen features granite counters, white shaker cabinetry, an island w/ ample storage and an incredible pantry + wine closet. Open concept main level with white stone wrapped gas fireplace and beautiful large & bright windows + easy access to the fenced back yard. Spa like vaulted primary bed & bath with double sinks, walk-in shower, and custom walk-in closet. High quality carpet upstairs, full guest bath, conveniently located laundry room, and nook perfect for your Peloton, desk, or reading nook. Tucked back in the cul-de-sac with easy park and trail access. Large garage w/ storage.

Welcome to your dream home! Built in 2022, this 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom beauty is situated on a bright and sunny lot, offering an abundance of natural light creating an open and airy feel. Main floor primary bedroom features a 5 piece bathroom and huge walk-in closet. The expansive family room upstairs provides the perfect space for entertaining, relaxing, working or creating a home theater. The spa-like bathrooms are designed for ultimate comfort and relaxation, and each bedroom is equipped with its own ductless mini-split system for personalized climate control. The home features durable vinyl plank flooring, sleek quartz countertops, ample storage and a cozy gas fireplace. Step outside to a low maintenance yard and lovely, covered patio.

Welcome to the premier Lake Whatcom condo you've been waiting for! With lake views from every room this single-level, 2 bedroom condo is steps to your dreams. Walking distance to the quiet & calm AM PM beach with kayak storage, marina with boat storage, golf course & all amenities offered in Sudden Valley including the pool, fitness center & clubhouse. Recently completely remodeled with new floors, countertops, cabinets, paint and top-of-the-line appliances. High-end trim package & doors. New bay window recently installed to take in the stunning lake views. Primary bedroom with private deck also with lake views! Building has been freshly resided & roof installed. Carport directly in front for easy parking. Live vacation life full-time!

Welcome to your dream home nestled between Bellingham & Ferndale with it's many amenities. This charming, single level residence offers a perfect blend of comfort, convenience & functionality. This 3 bd 1.5 bath 1421sq ft. home includes a spacious layout, inviting living room with a gas fireplace and huge picture window creating a warm, cozy atmosphere. Enjoy the large kitchen with tons of storage and counterspace. Step out to the lovely backyard and patio offering endless possibilities with a new garden shed for additional storage for your tools and outdoor equipment. Freshly painted exterior and newly hydroseeded lawn. The large 2 car garage, high efficiency furnace and AC make this home even better. Don't miss out on this gem of a home.
